msgstr ""
"MIS2 daraja turini Subordination Group ga moslashtirish\n"

# ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid ""
"Maps MIS2 organization level type codes to UZ Core Organizational "
"Subordination Group codes. MIS2 classifies healthcare facilities into "
"administrative levels, while OrganizationalSubordinationGroupCS groups "
"institutions by their administrative subordination (republican, territorial, "
"district/city, other ministries, private). The MIS2 level types Shahar "
"(Urban), Tuman (Area), and Mahalla (District) all fall under the combined "
"district-and-city administration category in the target."
msgstr ""
"MIS2 tashkilot darajasi turi kodlarini UZ Core Organizational Subordination "
"Group kodlariga moslashtiradi. MIS2 tibbiyot muassasalarini ma’muriy "
"darajalar bo‘yicha tasniflaydi, OrganizationalSubordinationGroupCS esa "
"muassasalarni ularning ma’muriy bo‘ysunuvi bo‘yicha guruhlaydi (respublika, "
"hududiy, tuman/shahar, boshqa vazirliklar, xususiy). MIS2 dagi Shahar, Tuman "
"va Mahalla daraja turlari maqsadli tizimdagi birlashtirilgan tuman-shahar "
"boshqaruvi toifasiga kiradi.\n"

# ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
msgid "MIS2 Medical Type to Organizational Structure"
msgstr ""
"MIS2 tibbiy turini Organizational Structure ga moslashtirish\n"

# ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid ""
"Maps MIS2 medical type codes to UZ Core Organizational Structure codes. MIS2 "
"classifies healthcare facilities into 45 medical types, while "
"OrganizationalStructureCS provides the Ministry of Health's detailed "
"classification of institution types."
msgstr ""
"MIS2 tibbiy tur kodlarini UZ Core Organizational Structure kodlariga "
"moslashtiradi. MIS2 tibbiyot muassasalarini 45 ta tibbiy turga tasniflaydi, "
"OrganizationalStructureCS esa Sog‘liqni saqlash vazirligi tomonidan "
"belgilangan muassasa turlarining batafsil tasnifini taqdim etadi.\n"

# ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
msgid "MIS2 Service Type to Organizational Service Group"
msgstr ""
"MIS2 xizmat turini Organizational Service Group ga moslashtirish\n"

# ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid ""
"Maps MIS2 service type codes to UZ Core Organizational Service Group codes. "
"MIS2 uses service type classification per organization, while "
"OrganizationalServiceGroupCS uses a single pre-combined classification. When "
"an organization has multiple MIS2 service types, the combination should be "
"considered to select the appropriate target code (e.g. Inpatient + "
"Outpatient together maps to III_100)."
msgstr ""
"MIS2 xizmat turi kodlarini UZ Core Organizational Service Group kodlariga "
"moslashtiradi. MIS2 har bir tashkilot bo‘yicha xizmat turi tasnifidan "
"foydalanadi, OrganizationalServiceGroupCS esa yagona oldindan "
"birlashtirilgan tasnifdan foydalanadi. Agar tashkilotda bir nechta MIS2 "
"xizmat turi mavjud bo‘lsa, tegishli maqsadli kodni tanlash uchun ularning "
"kombinatsiyasi hisobga olinishi kerak (masalan, Statsionar + ambulatoriya "
"birgalikda III_100 ga moslashtiriladi)."

